OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fclear spells continue as showers
OL,7,Fmostly die out during the evening.
OL,8,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,9,Fmainly dry with just the odd shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry in the north at first.
OL,12,FCloud and rain, some heavy, soon
OL,13,Fspread northeast. The rain becomes
OL,14,Flight and patchy during the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,17,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,18,FFriday. Bright spells and a few
OL,19,Fshowers on Saturday. Dry and bright on
OL,20,FSunday. Warm in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
